description:
Singer-songwriter Maya de Vitry talks about her Blueridge BR-143 guitar
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Maya de Vitry describes how she came to play a Blueridge BR-143 and why it’s the guitar most suitable for her songwriting, performing and touring.

Watch the full video here: https://youtu.be/gQfF62sO0wU
